          h2 Browse Libraries of Other Users
          p
            | You can browse through all the books Listed on this Platform. See What other are Reading
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Borrow Books to Read
          p
            | You can Borrow the books you just cant seem to move over. Given that book owner agrees.
        .col-sm-4
          h2 Lend your books
          p
            | Spread the love. Lend your book titles to other fellow readers. Biggest joy is spreading knowledge.
        .col-sm-4  
